data.description: Located in the sought-after Spring Lake community this 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage on a ½ acre lot is perfect for the buyer that is looking for space, peacefulness or room for a growing family.  Spacious bedrooms, large living area plus a bonus/family room (current owners are currently using this as their dining area), breakfast nook, in house laundry, plus a 19x9 screened lanai that extends the living area to the tranquil backyard for relaxation and enjoyment.  The Spring Lake community offers a variety of amenities from the Spring Lake International golf course, clubhouse, playground, tennis courts, pickleball facilities, “bark park” and picnic area. For fishing and outdoor enthusiasts, Lake Istokpoga’s public boat ramp is just minutes away.  Call today to schedule your private showing.
